column2: Hum Ko Mann Ki Shakti Dena
Logon Ke Ghar Mein Rahta Hoon
Machal Kar Jab Bhi Ankhon Se
Din Kuchh Aise Guzaarta Hai Koi
Aaj Phir Chaand Ki Peshaani Se Uthtaa Hai Dhuaan
Bas Ek Hi Sur Mein Ek Hi Laya Pe
Bas Ek Jhadge Kaa Lamha Thha
Dikhaaee Dete Hain In Lakeerein Mein Saaye Koi
Haan Mere Gham Toh Utha Leta Hai
Kabhi Kabhi Jab Main Baith Jaata Hoon
Kal Ki Raat Giri Thhi Shabnam
Kis Qadar Seedha Sehal Saaf Hai Rasta Dekho
Mitaa Do Saare Nishaan Ke Thhe Tum
Raat Bhar Sard Hava Chalti Rahi
Saans Lena Bhi Kaisi Aadat Hai-Gulzar
Sab Kuchh Vaise Hi Chalta Hai
Sirf Ehsaas Ke Paas Ho Tum
Sur Vahi Saazon Pe Chalti Huee Aawaaz Vahi
Takiye Pe Tere Voh Sar Ka
Worth Jo Scent Hai Mitti Ka
Yeh Kaisi Umr Mein Aakar Mili Ho Tum
Tum Pukar Lo Tumhara Intezar Hai
Meri Jaan Mujhe Jaan Na Kaho
Jab Bhi Yeh Dil Udas Hota Hai
Aise Danton Mein Ungli Dabao Nahin
Hawaon Pe Likhdo Hawaon Ke Naam
Ek Din Sapne Mein Dekha Sapna
Phir Wohi Raat Hai Khwab Ki
Hamne Dekhi Hai Un Ankhon Ki
Do Nainon Mein Ansoo Bhare Hai
Ek Baat Kahoon Gar Mano Tum
Aajkal Paon Zameen Par Nahin Padte
Dabe Labon Se Kabhi Jo Koi Salam Le
Tum Aa Gaye Ho Noor Aa Gaya
